## Project Objective

The objective of this project is to build a real-world SOC environment for learning security monitoring, threat detection, incident investigation, log analysis, security automation, and threat intelligence integration. The project demonstrates how security teams collect logs, detect attacks, investigate alerts, automate responses, and improve overall security visibility using industry-standard cybersecurity tools.
